{
  "stem": "6258.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we heard that they are-- we knew that when they-- the German are doing some kind of an action or transportation or deportation, there is always killing, stealing, beating, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not that I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- well, they were more or less-- at least they were not so hateful toward us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were lucky, all of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the largest percentage of people who survived from Krakow, they were this one who were, at this worst time, in Fliegerhorst, and not in-- in the ghetto in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the barracks, where-- we were the girls'-- womans' barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had rooms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were about 20 girls in one room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were double [INAUDIBLE] we have.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, it was like a YMCA summer camp, one could say--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the barracks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we were sleeping on the double beds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we had--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, straw mattresses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had our own from home, places, beddings, this and that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, of course, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was so that we were--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were allowed--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to take.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, sure, but depending how much space there is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then when-- when the-- get camp from Plaszow to Fliegerhorst, they painted our-- if you know, everything, dresses, like stripes, yellow stripes this--",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came later on when we become part of-- part of Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was usually we get up at 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And about 7 o'clock we got our-- I don't know, some breakfast or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before 8 o'clock--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bread and margarine or bread and cheese or bread and-- and sometimes sausage and-- and these things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we work-- It depends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Usually some people, we came between-- from 8 o'clock between 12:00 and 1:00",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
